caption.text: Look at these hens. They were born only for one reason. They were born only for live in that lumbers and spawn for years. After that, they will be eaten by you. Poor hens. We are going to die but we may live forever and enjoy Him forever. We'll reach our ultimate purpose and meaning of life. And that's not because our goodness but because of Him.
